{"model":"gemini-2.5-flash-preview-05-20","temperature":0,"messages":[{"role":"system","content":"You are given a request from a user to a AI coding assistant, and your task is to categorize the user's natural language based on the request. Report the language of the user in English, so for example you might return "English" or "Spanish" or "French" or "German" or "Italian" or "Portuguese" or "Russian" or "Chinese" or "Japanese" or "Korean" or "Arabic" or "Hebrew" or "Turkish" or "Dutch" or "Polish" or "Romanian" or "Czech" or "Slovak" or "Hungarian" or "Bulgarian" or "Croatian" or "Serbian" or "Maltese" or "Estonian" or "Latvian" or "Lithuanian" or "Slovenian" or "Bosnian" or "Montenegrin" or "Albanian" or "Macedonian".

Do not categorize dialects or other variations of the language. Don't use abbreviations and don't use special characters.

If you cannot determine the user's language, return the category name "Other"."},{"role":"user","content":"Please analyze the following request and then categorize the user's language.
